snippet.textDisplay: As an ethnic Chinese myself (overseas), it'd be ridiculous to call me racist. Rather it's anger stemming from the fact this isn't the first time such pandemic originated from China. Dialled back 17 years ago we also had the SARS thanks to the mainland chinese. Whether be it the conoravirus or SARS, they were allowed to happen because unsanitary conditions of the wildlife markets, where different species of animals are cramped together. Last time it was civet cats and this time believed to have come from the bats or snakes or cross-infection. Whatever the case, this was because the mainland chinese still keep their dirty habits of wildlife meat consumption and unhygienic personal habits like spitting anywhere and everywhere. Obviously we were mad at them because they seem not to have learnt anything from SARS and kept up their habits. There are so many ways of preparing pork, beef, chicken, fish tastefully and these are traditional poultry, why would they even want to try animals like bats, snakes, wolves, rodents etc, not to mention dogs and cats which they slaughtered in the cruellest ways! I have no sympathy for them 2nd time round. They and their govt have not been rigorous in banning the sales and consumption of wildlife. Their irresponsible actions resulted in racist acts and reactions on anyone who look east asian in other countries, which means people from places like Taiwan, s Korea, Japan, Singapore etc also end up on the whip because of them. In fact, we are the peoples directly affected by them due to our geographical locations. If they have learnt anything this time (and happened during CNY), the next thing they should do is to ban wildlife market from China permanently. This goes for other countries that I know which also consume wildlife, such as Cambodia, Thailand, Philippines, etc. If some western countries are also doing it, the same message applies to you. Twice it came from China, the next time could be from either one of those countries mentioned. Then I say same to these countries too. Retribution from those animals you consumed and Karma dished out by some Almighty! China, hope this will wake you up for good and that you will remember for life because this has been a most unforgettable and dismal CNY for you!
